Subject: [PATCH 0003/4706] mm/fault, drm/i915: Use pagefault_disabled() to
 check for disabled pagefaults

commit 32d8206725bcf6e3ce7832ac39e61a6ecfd558db upstream

Now that the pagefault disabled counter is in place, we can replace
the in_atomic() check by a pagefault_disabled() checks.

